  },
  {
    "start": 35.0,
    "end": 39.0,
    "text": "I've seen the bridge, the bridge of love,"
  },
  {
    "start": 39.0,
    "end": 44.0,
    "text": "And they build it high, and they build it strong,"
  },
  {
    "start": 44.0,
    "end": 46.0,
    "text": "Strong enough to hold"
  },
  {
    "start": 46.0,
    "end": 50.0,
    "text": "The weight of time, love enough to leave"
  },
  {
    "start": 50.0,
    "end": 54.0,
    "text": "Some of us behind, and every one of us"
  },
  {
    "start": 54.0,
    "end": 57.0,
    "text": "Has to face that day"
  },
  {
    "start": 57.0,
    "end": 61.0,
    "text": "To cross the bridge or get fed away"
  },
  {
    "start": 61.0,
    "end": 66.0,
    "text": "And every one of us that ever came to play"
  },
  {
    "start": 66.0,
    "end": 73.0,
    "text": "Has to cross the bridge or say the prayer"
  },
  {
    "start": 73.0,
    "end": 79.0,
    "text": "And the bridge, it shines"
  },
  {
    "start": 79.0,
    "end": 83.0,
    "text": "Oh come, come on"
  },
  {
    "start": 83.0,
    "end": 87.0,
